  "original_title": "\u0da0\u0dd3\u0db1 \u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc4\u0db8\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dcf \u0db8\u0dd4\u0dbb \u0dc3\u0d82\u0da0\u0dcf\u0dbb \u0d9a\u0dbd\u0dcf\u0db4\u0dba \u0db4\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dcf \u0d89\u0dc4\u0dc5 \u0daf\u0dd0\u0db8\u0dd3\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "An increase in Chinese air force patrols across the region",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "China's People's Liberation Army (PLA) air force said it had conducted island patrols to protect national sovereignty and territorial integrity.",
        "\"Defending our motherland is the sacred mission of the PLA Air Force,\" PLA Air Force spokesman Senior Colonel Shen Jinke said at a press conference in Beijing. Namely.",
        "Responding to a reporter's question about the Air Force's patrols around the Taiwan region, Shen said the Air Force has conducted multiple warplane patrols around the island of Taiwan to hone and improve its ability to protect national sovereignty and territorial integrity.",
        "\"The Air Force has firm determination, full confidence and sufficient capability to protect national sovereignty and territorial integrity,\" Shen said.",
        "Also, the PLA's patrols in the South China Sea will enhance its ability to deal with all kinds of security threats, Shen said."
      ],
